{
  "stem": "11589.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 132.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the order of Stalin was in those days, they can't walk, just leave them there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Shoot them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They needed people here to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If they are sick, we don't need them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was the law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt bad about this kid, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was strong, thanks to God.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- and I was able to give him a hand, put my hand under his waist, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I carried him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to save him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe he'll feel better tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then winter came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things were cold, didn't have enough to wear things, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We made miles and miles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we walked there days and weeks, for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Finally, they took us to a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then were all strangers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never saw all there one of the kids that I left my home town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us to that train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the last of the traveling, you know, that we traveled, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's [? the whole ?] [? voyage. ?] Did they feed you?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did the Russians feed you along the way?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very badly, very badly, just to stay alive, just to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The reason is because, first of all, they don't know how to handle it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Secondly, they were poor, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, they don't know how to deal with this kind of situation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we suffered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The dirt in the train, and all that, you know, for, for weeks-- you know, it's enclosed, no air, nothing, until we arrived to a Siberian town named Omsk.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Omsk is located in Northern Siberia, you know, Siberia.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
